n%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20yet%20to%20sink%20in%20and%20things%20you%20are%20talking%20about%2C%20if%20it%20happens%20organically%2C%20it%20will%20happen.%20We%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20digest%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20India%20U-19%20left-arm%20pacer%2C%20who%20made%20the%20difference%20with%20a%20brilliant%20Super%20Over%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumni%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Cornell%20University%20and%20a%20senior%20techie%20(coder)%20at%20the%20Oracle%2C%20Netravalkar%20juggled%20academics%20and%20cricket%20with%20aplomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20felt%20the%20pressure.%20When%20you%20love%20something%2C%20it%20is%20never%20a%20job%20for%20you.%20So%20when%20I%20am%20out%20there%20on%20the%20field%2C%20I%20love%20bowling%20and%20trying%20to%20out-think%20a%20batter.%20When%20I%20am%20coding%2C%20I%20love%20doing%20that%20and%20hence%20it%20never%20feels%20like%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20left-arm%20seamer%2C%20who%20has%20suddenly%20become%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town%2C%20couldn't%20have%20put%20it%20more%20lucidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActually%2C%20we%20just%20flew%20down%20from%20Dallas%20to%20New%20York.%20I%20will%20be%20honest%20that%20it%20has%20been%20quite%20overwhelming.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20personally%20thank%20each%20and%20everyone%20for%20their%20lovely%20messages.%20I%20feel%20blessed%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20could%20sense%20the%20gratitude%20in%20his%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20was%20the%20strategy%20for%20the%20Super%20Over%20and%20when%20did%20he%20come%20to%20know%20that%20he%20would%20be%20bowling%3F%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20pre-decided%20and%20only%20after%20the%20regulation%2020%20overs%20did%20skipper%20(Monank%20Patel)%20and%20coach%20(Stuart%20Law)%20informed%20me%20about%20it.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20them%20for%20showing%20faith%20in%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20then%20gave%20an%20insight%20into%20the%20US%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20plan%20was%20simple%20that%20I%20will%20try%20and%20bowl%20wide%20yorkers%20to%20the%20right%20handers%20and%20try%20to%20keep%20it%20out%20of%20his%20range%20as%20the%20boundary%20on%20that%20side%20was%20bigger.%20First%20ball%20the%20batter%20shifted%20and%20didn't%20get%20a%20wide%20and%20second%20ball%2C%20he%20stayed%20rooted%20and%20connected%2C%20and%20then%2C%20I%20got%20a%20couple%20of%20wides%2C%20as%20I%20was%20trying%20for%20wide%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20must%20say%20that%2018%20runs%20helped%20and%20all%20those%20extra%20runs%20that%20Harmeet%20(Singh)%20and%20Aaron%20(Jones)%20ran%2C%20helped.%20Basically%2C%20if%20you%20are%20defending%20around%2020%2C%20all%20you%20need%20is%20three%20good%20balls%2C%20and%20the%20job%20is%20done.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20matches%20I%20have%20played.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20Netravalkar%20would%20also%20say%20matter%20of%20factly%20that%20while%20things%20are%20looking%20up%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20pursue%20cricket%20as%20profession%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20for%20him%2C%20his%20day%20job%20at%20Oracle%20is%20still%20his%20primary%20source%20of%20%26quot%3Bbread%20and%20butter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20part%20is%20that%20I%20have%20got%20very%20supportive%20bosses%20at%20Oracle%20and%20I%20am%20allowed%20to%20work%20remotely%20when%20I%20am%20on%20tour%2C%20playing%20for%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20on%20match%20days%2C%20I%20am%20excused%20from%20work%20but%20then%20there%20are%20scheduled%20project%20meetings%20which%20warrants%20my%20presence%20and%20then%20I%20work%20my%20practice%20schedule%20accordingly.%20I%20would%20also%20thank%20US%20Cricket%20board%20as%20they%20also%20are%20flexible%20if%20I%20have%20meetings%20lined%20up.%26quot%3B%20His%20is%20a%20fascinating%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20when%20I%20play%20local%20matches%20or%20club%20games%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20I%20have%20often%20logged%20in%20for%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20lunch%20break%20and%20people%20have%20been%20very%20accommodating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Oracle%2C%20they%20all%20know%20by%20now%20I%20play%20cricket%20and%20everyone%20is%20happy%20to%20support.%20I%20work%20in%20team%20Oracle%20text%20and%20I%20am%20primarily%20a%20coder%2C%20who%20works%20on%20SQL%20and%20C%20(programming%20languages)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20full-time%20cricket%20career%20in%20the%20United%20States%3F%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20Major%20League%20Contracts%2C%20those%20are%20good%20and%20you%20can%20have%20a%20full-time%20cricket%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMinor%20League%20Cricket%20is%20also%20seeing%20an%20upswing%20but%20another%20avenue%20is%20some%20weekend%20'Pop-Up'%20tournaments%2C%20basically%20played%20from%20Friday%20to%20Sunday%20in%20Houston%2C%20Florida%20where%20you%20can%20actually%20earn%20well.%26quot%3B%20Come%20June%2012%2C%20and%20Netravalkar%20will%20be%20facing%20the%20Indian%20team%20and%20he%20is%20quite%20emotional%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20all%20of%20them%20and%20Surya%20(Yadav)%20and%20myself%20have%20played%20together%20for%20Mumbai%20U15s%2C%20U-17%2C%20U-19s.%20It%20is%20so%20good%20to%20see%20what%20he%20has%20achieved%20and%20it%20will%20be%20nice%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20them.%20Playing%20against%20India%20would%20be%20truly%20emotional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717828200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flvhgfdm8_saurabh-netravalkar-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fs