that%20shower%20caps%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20shoes.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20hotel%20guests%20can%20also%20use%20a%20shower%20cap%20like%20a%20remote%20cover%20to%20avoid%20germs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20attendant%20revealed%20that%20hotel%20rooms%20don't%20really%20need%20a%20room%20key%20for%20power.%20Any%20card%20can%20keep%20the%20electricity%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717824780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fao2arq58_hotel-generic_625x300_17_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fflight-attendant-shares-travel-hack-to-never-forget-valuables-in-hotel-room-5843874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20flight%20attendant%20has%20shared%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame-changing%26quot%3B%20tip%20to%20ensure%20hotel%20guests%20never%20forget%20valuables%20in%20the%20room%20when%20they%20check%20out.%20Esther%20Sturrus%20shared%20the%20travel%20hack%20in%20a%20TikTok%20video%2C%20which%20is%20now%20going%20viral%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fflight-attendant-shares-travel-hack-to-never-forget-valuables-in-hotel-room-5843874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fflight-attendant-shares-travel-hack-to-never-forget-valuables-in-hotel-room-5843874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fflight-attendant-shares-travel-hack-to-never-forget-valuables-in-hotel-room-5843874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bombarded%20By%20Questions%20On%20New%20York%20Pitch%2C%20India%20Coach%20Makes%20Stance%20Clear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20time%20in%20as%20many%20games%2C%20a%20low-scoring%20match%20was%20played%20in%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20at%20New%20York.%20After%20Sri%20Lanka%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2077%20by%20South%20Africa%2C%20India's%20bowlers%20were%20fearsome%20and%20relentless%20in%20bundling%20out%20Ireland%20for%2096.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%20in%20New%20York%20once%20again%20became%20a%20huge%20talking%20point%20%E2%80%93%20there%20was%20excessive%20movement%20and%20variable%20bounce%20kept%20the%20batters%20guessing%2C%20though%20some%20like%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20took%20blows%20in%20a%20rather%20comfortable%20eight-wicket%20win%20for%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20Rathour%2C%20India's%20batting%20coach%2C%20admitted%20the%20pitch%20at%20New%20York%20for%20their%20first%20Group%20A%20game%20was%20challenging%20for%20the%20batters%2C%20but%20felt%20the%20side%20is%20ready%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20tough%20conditions%2C%20especially%20with%20their%20next%20game%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209%20at%20the%20same%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20challenging%20wicket%20as%20far%20as%20batting%20is%20concerned%20but%20this%20is%20what%20we%20have%20so%20we%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20Like%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20we%20have%20enough%20skills%20and%20experience%20in%20the%20batting%20group%20especially%20to%20deal%20with%20that.%20We%20have%20enough%20good%20batters%20who%20can%20manage%20to%20bat%20well%20on%20any%20kind%20of%20surface.%20I%20think%20that%20has%20been%20our%20strength%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20can%20adapt%20really%20well%20to%20different%20conditions%2C%20and%20I%20think%20on%20this%20surface%20you%20really%20need%20to%20adapt%20well%20and%20take%20it%20head-on%20and%20not%20worry%20about%20it%20too%20much%20and%20you're%20right%20-%20we%20have%20everybody%20fit%2C%20and%20they're%20all%20looking%20good.%20They're%20all%20batting%20well%3B%20so%20it's%20a%20good%20space%20to%20be%20as%20a%20batting%20coach%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rathour%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20how%20India%20are%20well-equipped%20in%20terms%20of%20adaptability%20on%20seeing%20the%20conditions%20offered%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20playing%20T20%20cricket%20together%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20our%20batting%20unit%20is%20very%20adaptable.%20We%20adapt%20to%20different%20conditions%20very%20well%20and%20that%20has%20been%20our%20strength%20for%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20too%20concerned.%20We%20have%20played%20good%20tournaments%3B%20IPL%20is%20a%20competitive%20tournament%20and%20we%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20skills.%20Adapting%20to%20the%20conditions%2C%20every%20team%20will%20have%20to%20adapt%2C%20not%20just%20us.%20I%20think%20that%20gives%20us%20an%20edge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20toss%20become%20a%20little%20too%20crucial%20on%20a%20challenging%20Test-match%20style%20pitch%20like%20the%20one%20served%20for%20Wednesday's%20match%2C%20Rathour%20replied%20in%20the%20affirmative.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20toss%20is%20crucial%20in%20conditions%20like%20these%2C%20but%20fortunately%2C%20we%20won%20the%20toss%20here%20so%20it%20was%20a%20great%20start%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20again%20control%20that.%20So%20even%20if%20we%20lose%20the%20toss%20and%20we%20have%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20we%20still%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20pitch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20welcome%20change%20in%20India's%20batting%20strategy%20has%20been%20slotting%20in%20left-handed%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Rishabh%20Pant%20at%20three.%20In%20the%20warm-up%20game%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pant%20made%20a%20fluent%2052%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20could%20occupy%20number%20three%20slot%20for%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20Ireland%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20was%20also%20his%20comeback%20game%20in%20in