5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-top-streaming-service-headwinds-competition-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20simple%2C%20five-word%20line%20that%20appears%20onscreen%20near%20the%20top%20of%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20the%20seven-part%20series%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20true%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20which%20became%20a%20sensation%20after%20premiering%20on%20Netflix%20in%20April%2C%20was%20created%20by%20Scottish%20comedian%20Richard%20Gadd%2C%20who%20also%20stars%20as%20Donny%20Dunn.%20Dunn%20is%20based%20on%20Gadd%2C%20who%20has%20said%20the%20show%20depicts%20a%20real-life%20experience%20in%20which%20he%20was%20stalked%20early%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20show%20premiered%2C%20internet%20sleuths%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20pleas%20from%20the%20cast%20%E2%80%94%20tried%20to%20find%20the%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20stalker%20character%2C%20%26quot%3BMartha%20Scott.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-piers-morgan-fiona-harvey-lied-youtube-interview-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Piers%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20Harvey%20admitted%20she%20had%20known%20Gadd%20but%20denied%20stalking%20him%20or%20ever%20being%20convicted%20of%20stalking.%20She%20also%20said%20she%20was%20considering%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffiona-harvey-stalker-martha-scott-baby-reindeer-sued-netflix-millions-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20action%20against%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.928856%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.928856.1.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20Thursday%2C%20Harvey%20accused%20Netflix%20of%20defamation%20and%20intentional%20affliction%20of%20emotional%20distress%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20misrepresented%20her%20and%20made%20her%20easily%20identifiable%2C%20resulting%20in%20reputation%20damages.%20The%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20does%20not%20name%20Gadd%20as%20a%20defendant%2C%20seeks%20more%20than%20%24170%20million%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendants%20told%20these%20lies%2C%20and%20never%20stopped%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20better%20story%20than%20the%20truth%2C%20and%20better%20stories%20made%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Netflix%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20defend%20this%20matter%20vigorously%20and%20to%20stand%20by%20Richard%20Gadd's%20right%20to%20tell%20his%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETre%20Lovell%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20entertainment%20attorney%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lovellfirm.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Lovell%20Firm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20thinks%20Harvey%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20strong%20case%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20her%20complaint%20if%20she%20can%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20show%20made%20her%20readily%20identifiable%20and%20made%20false%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Gunning%20as%20Martha%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20and%20Fiona%20Harvey%20on%20%26quot%3BPiers%20Morgan%20Uncensored.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6662daedcc442a2f676ef8f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Gunning%20as%20Martha%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20and%20Fiona%20Harvey%20on%20%26quot%3BPiers%20Morgan%20Uncensored.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%2FPiers%20Morgan%2FUncensored%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a12f171e-4889-40a2-83b8-6d6e090e7eba%5C%22%3E'Baby%20Reindeer'%20and%20fictionalized%20truth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorneys%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20noted%20that%20fictionalized%20dramas%20in%20which%20a%20real%20person%20is%20depicted%20generally%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20work%20is%20not%20100%25%20true%20and%20that%20aspects%20have%20been%20changed%20or%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20true%20story%26quot%3B%20is%20notably%20different%20than%20when%20a%20work%20states%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Binspired%20by%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%26quot%3B%20a%20true%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20does%20include%20a%20disclaimer%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20credits%20that%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20program%20is%20based%20on%20real%20events%3A%20however%20certain%20characters%2C%20names%2C%20incidents%2C%20locations%2C%20and%20dialogue%20have%20been%20fictionalized%20for%20dramatic%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Lovell%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20the%20average%20viewer%20would%20notice%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20argument%20will%20be%2C%20'Well%2C%20a%20consumer%20is%20looking%20at%20that%20and%20thinking%20everything%20in%20this%20is%20true%2C%20and%20you're%20purposely%20hiding%20the%20disclaimer%20about%20fictionalizing%20the%20characters%20on%20the%20back%20end%2C'%26quot%3B%20Camron%20Dowlatshahi%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20entertainment%20attorney%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmsdlawyers.com%2Fcamron-dowlatshahi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMills%20Sadat%20Dowlat%20LLP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThen%20when%20you%20follow%20it%20up%20with%20press%20saying%20everything%20is%20true%2C%20then%20that's%20where%20the%20issue%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGadd%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian%20in%20April%20that%20the%20show%20was%20%26quot%3Btweaked%20slightly%20to%20create%20dramatic%20climaxes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20emotionally%20true%2C%20obviously%3A%20I%20was%20severely%20stalked%20and%20severely%20abused.%20But%20we%20wanted%20it%20to%20exist%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20art%2C%20as%20well%20as%20protect%20the%20people%20it's%20based%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205686755-d3e5-48e0-af53-800aafd8ec1e%5C%22%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20internet%20sleuths%20to%20find%20Harvey%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGadd%2C%20who%20urged%20fans%20not%20to%20try%20to%20identify%20the%20real%20people%20the%20story%20is%20based%20on%2C%20has%20also%20said%20they%20changed%20the%20Martha%20character%20so%20much%20that%20the%20real-life%20person%20she%20was%20based%20on%20would%20likely%20not%20recognize%20herself%20in%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20been%20borrowed%20is%20an%20emotional%20truth%2C%20not%20a%20fact-by-fact%20profile%20of%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20Gadd%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq-magazine.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fbaby-reindeer-netflix-richard-gadd-interview%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_social-type%3Downed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGQ%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20her%20lawsuit%2C%20Harvey%20claims%20that%20she%20and%20the%20Martha%20character%20several%20similarities%2C%20including%20their%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20nationality%2C%20and%20profession.%20The%20show%20even%20uses%20some%20of%20the%20same%20strange%20phrasing%20that%20Harvey%20appeared%20to%20use%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FFionaHarvey2014%2Fstatus%2F514416588645494785%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20directed%20at%20Gadd%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20post%20that%20fans%20quickly%20found%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvey%20accused%20Netflix%20of%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20conceal%20her%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDowlatshahi%20said%20he%20thinks%20Netflix%20has%20some%20decent%20arguments%20against%20that%20accusation%2C%20including%20that%20they%20used%20a%20different%20name%20and%20changed%20some%20facts%20about%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Lovell%20believes%20that%20Netflix%20could've%20done%20much%20more%2C%20including%20changing%20basic%20details%20about%20the%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Gadd%20as%20Donny%20Dunn%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661f975320b15f0ff428a744%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERichard%20Gadd%20as%20Donny%20Dunn%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b31b970-d0ad-4709-9274-f81a28fd45f0%5C%22%3EHarvey%20may%20end%20up%20getting%20something%20from%20Netflix%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDowlatshahi%20called%20the%20amount%20of%20damages%20Harvey%20seeks%20%26quot%3Bexorbitant%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20he%20doubts%20she%20could%20get%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Lovell%20noted%20a%20string%20of%20recent%20high-profile%20defamation%20cases%20in%20which%20plaintiffs%20have%20been%20awarded%20huge%20sums%2C%20including%20the%20two%20Georgia%20election%20workers%20awarded%20%24148%20million%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%20against%20Rudy%20Giuliani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20lawyers%20agreed%20it%20was%20highly%20unlikely%20the%20case%20would%20go%20to%20trial%20and%20that%20Netflix%20would%20more%20than%20likely%20settle%2C%20as%20the%20company%20did%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20filed%20over%20the%202019%20series%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fnetflix-central-park-five-lawsuit-duvernay-33e090919d183c32537cc952ef3031ff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20See%20Us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovell%20said%20Netflix%20would%20likely%20try%20to%20argue%20Harvey%20was%20already%20a%20public%20figure%2C%20which%20can%20raise%20the%20bar%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%20by%20requiring%20proof%20of%20%26quot%3Bactual%20malice%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%20that%20the%20defendant%20knew%20the%20claims%20made%20were%20false%20or%20had%20a%20reckless%20disregard%20for%20the%20truth.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20would%20likely%20argue%20that%20Harvey%20was%20not%20readily%20identifiable%20and%20that%20they%20acted%20reasonably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20added%20that%20the%20claims%20Harvey%20is%20accusing%20Netflix%20of%20making%20up%20about%20her%20%E2%80%94%20committing%20actual%20crimes%20and%20serving%20prison%20time%20%E2%80%94%20are%20about%20as%20straightforward%20as%20they%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Harvey%20can%20demonstrate%20that%20she%20was%20readily%20identifiable%20in%20the%20show%20and%20that%20Netflix%20made%20up%20those%20claims%20about%20her%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20worst%20type%20of%20defamation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-lawsuit-netflix-true-story-claim-fiona-harvey-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717817751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661e43ac49058e66935650b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-lawsuit-netflix-true-story-claim-fiona-harvey-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix's%20line%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20story%26quot%3B%20could%20hurt%20the%20company%20in%20the%20defamation%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20Fiona%20Harvey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-lawsuit-netflix-true-story-claim-fiona-harvey-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revisitin