TV%20Swap%20feature%20(more%20on%20that%20below)%2C%20the%20Ace's%20setup%20experience%20is%20as%20slick%20and%20smooth%20as%20you'd%20expect%20from%20a%20brand%20of%20Sonos'%20pedigree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpening%20the%20box%20reveals%20a%20fuzzy%20gray%20case%20made%20from%2075%25%20recycled%20plastic%20bottles.%20Unzip%20it%2C%20and%20you'll%20find%20a%20minimalist%20pair%20of%20matte%20headphones%20in%20black%20or%20Soft%20White%20wrapped%20around%20a%20bean-shaped%20pouch.%20Designed%20to%20harbor%20the%20Ace's%20dual%20USB-C%20cables%20for%20wired%20playback%20and%20charging%2C%20the%20pouch%20attaches%20via%20a%20strong%20magnet%20at%20the%20case's%20center%2C%20efficiently%20utilizing%20the%20space.%20The%20whole%20layout%20feels%20equally%20aimed%20at%20style%20and%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20headphones%20themselves%20borrow%20aesthetic%20touches%20from%20rivals%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6f20e5313e131c16e6f5c0f1fe75d236e3a602c408332ecf90130e2e048decb1%26postID%3D6663095ee01a10ede1c25f21%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBose-QuietComfort-Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones%252Fdp%252FB0CCZ1L489%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fapple-airpods-max-review%5C%22%3EApple%20AirPods%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20with%20a%20Sonos%20twist%2C%20bearing%20the%20same%20elegantly%20stripped-down%20design%20cues%20found%20across%20all%20Sonos%20products.%20From%20the%20Ace's%20sleek%20rounded%20ear%20cups%20and%20laser-etched%20logo%20to%20their%20steel%20arms%20and%20cushy%2C%20vegan-leather%20pads%2C%20this%20is%20a%20familiar%20package%20that%20still%20manages%20to%20strike%20its%20own%20chord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20right%20ear%20cup%20are%20dual%20control%20buttons%2C%20including%20a%20multi-function%20%26quot%3Bcontent%20key%26quot%3B%20for%20playback%20and%20volume%20via%20a%20mix%20of%20taps%20and%20slides.%20There's%20also%20an%20adjacent%20key%20to%20swap%20between%20noise%20canceling%20and%20transparency%20modes.%20The%20two%20keys%20are%20easily%20distinguishable%20by%20touch%20for%20error-free%20control%20in%20nearly%20any%20setting.%20On%20the%20left%20cup%20is%20the%20power%2Fpairing%20key%20and%20a%20USB-C%20input%20for%20charging%20and%20wired%20playback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDownloading%20the%20Sonos%20app%20helps%20you%20quickly%20pair%20the%20headphones%20to%20your%20mobile%20device%20and%20add%20them%20to%20your%20list%20of%20Sonos%20devices%20where%20you%20can%20monitor%20status%20and%20battery%20life.%20Tapping%20the%20Settings%20icon%20lets%20you%20adjust%20features%20like%20bass%20and%20treble%2C%20head%20tracking%20for%20spatial%20audio%20effects%2C%20and%20multi-point%20audio%20to%20pair%20the%20headphones%20to%20a%20second%20device%20like%20a%20laptop%20or%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfortable%20fit%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20flexible%20band%20and%20fluffy%20pads%20give%20the%20Ace%20an%20edge%20in%20comfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sonos%20Ace's%20cushions%20and%20earcups%20are%20shown%20on%20a%20black%20console.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66638135e079049018172d89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ace%20are%20incredibly%20comfortable%20to%20wear.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EComfort%20is%20always%20subjective%2C%20but%20we%20can%20say%20without%20hesitation%20that%20the%20Ace%20are%20the%20most%20comfortable%20noise-canceling%20headphones%20we've%20encountered%2C%20beating%20out%20favorites%20like%20Bose's%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsony-wh-1000xm5-wireless-noise-cancelling-headphones-review%5C%22%3ESony%20WH-1000XM5%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20a%20week%20of%20wearing%20the%20Ace%20nearly%20all%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20we%20rarely%20experienced%20an%20inkling%20of%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrankly%2C%20we're%20not%20sure%20how%20Sonos%20did%20it.%20At%20313%20grams%2C%20the%20Ace%20are%20lighter%20than%20Apple's%20AirPods%20Max%2C%20but%20still%20outweigh%20both%20Bose%20and%20Sony's%20top%20models%20by%20a%20good%2060%20grams.%20You%20can%20definitely%20feel%20the%20heft%20as%20you%20swing%20your%20head%20around%2C%20but%20somehow%20between%20their%20ultra-soft%20pads%20and%20taut%20yet%20judicious%20clamping%20force%2C%20they%20manage%20to%20pull%20off%20the%20proverbial%20headphone%20trick%20of%20nearly%20disappearing%20on%20your%20head%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fit%20is%20also%20quite%20stable%2C%20staying%20put%20even%20on%20light%20hikes%20and%20other%20semi-rigorous%20activities.%20Without%20an%20IP%20certification%20for%20water%20resistance%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20recommend%20the%20Ace%20for%20sweaty%20jogs%20or%20gym%20regimens%2C%20but%20they're%20excellent%20companions%20for%20nearly%20any%20other%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sound%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20sound%20is%20rich%2C%20smooth%2C%20and%20detailed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20Sonos%20Ace%20headphones%20resting%20on%20top%20of%20their%20case.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66638180a2a35d0ca376ff0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAudio%20performance%20is%20on%20par%20with%20other%20top%20wireless%20headphones%20in%20this%20price%20range.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace%20offer%20a%20smooth%20and%20mellow%20sound%20signature.%20They%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20digging%20up%20lush%20and%20vivid%20instrumental%20timbres%2C%20all%20spread%20across%20a%20deep%20and%20expansive%20soundstage.%20The%20overall%20performance%20stacks%20up%20well%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best-sounding%20headphones%20in%20their%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace%20do%20exhibit%20a%20darker%20tonal%20color%20than%20you'll%20find%20in%20rivals%20like%20the%20spritely%20Bose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra.%20But%20this%20doesn't%20affect%20the%20Ace's%20talent%20for%20exposing%20fine%20details.%20Horns%20are%20breathy%20and%20full.%20Strings%20are%20smooth%20and%20lush.%20Acoustic%20guitars%20ring%20with%20a%20golden%20sheen.%20The%20ability%20to%20precisely%20place%20all%20these%20instruments%20in%20the%20mix%20may%20be%20the%20Ace's%20most%20impressive%20sonic%20feature%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20explore%20each%20instrument%20independently%20or%20simply%20sit%20back%20and%20let%20them%20wash%20over%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20some%20sparkle%20in%20the%20treble%20for%20pristine%20clarity%20in%20high-flying%20percussion%20and%20loads%20of%20definition%20in%20instruments%20like%20buzzy%20synths%20and%20distorted%20electric%20guitars.%20At%20the%20other%20end%2C%20bass%20is%20full%20and%20punchy%20without%20being%20overwhelming.%20Unlike%20many%20headphones%20we%20test%2C%20the%20bass%20is%20fairly%20balanced%20by%20default%2C%20though%20we%20still%20dropped%20it%20down%20a%20notch%20or%20two%20in%20the%20EQ%20settings%20to%20clear%20up%20space%20in%20the%20soundstage.%20We%20also%20turned%20off%20the%20Loudness%20setting%2C%20which%20tended%20to%20make%20things%20sound%20a%20bit%20boomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20occasion%2C%20we%20wished%20for%20a%20bit%20more%20presence%20and%20clarity%20in%20vocals%20and%20dialogue%2C%20particularly%20when%20listening%20to%20podcasts%2C%20but%20we%20never%20struggled%20to%20hear%20minute%20details%20like%20vocal%20fry%20or%20room%20echos%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20notice%20sounds%20we'd%20missed%20in%20previous%20listens.%20Hardwiring%20the%20Ace%20via%20a%20USB-C-to-3.5mm%20cable%20offers%20even%20better%20definition%2C%20including%20support%20for%20lossless%20audio%20at%20up%20to%2016-bit%2F48Hz%20resolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace%20supports%20head%20tracking%20for%20stereo%20content%2C%20which%20keeps%20the%20sound%20anchored%20when%20you%20turn%20your%20head%20to%20mimic%20the%20effect%20of%20listening%20to%20speakers%20positioned%20in%20a%20fixed%20location.%20This%20is%20also%20supported%20with%20Dolby%20Atmos%203D%20audio%20when%20synced%20with%20an%20Arc%20soundbar%2C%20but%20we%20couldn't%20get%20that%20feature%20to%20work.%20However%2C%20with%20stereo%20content%2C%20head%20tracking%20works%20similarly%20to%20rivals%2C%20effectively%20simulating%20a%20home%20theater%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Noise-canceling%20performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise-canceling%20and%20transparency%20modes%20are%20phenomenal%2C%20aside%20from%20one%20hiccup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20Sonos%20Ace%20headphones%20next%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20Bose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666381cee079049018172d95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ace%20(left)%20next%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20Bose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20headphones%20(right).%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace's%20incredible%20noise%20canceling%20is%20a%20triumph%20worth%20celebrating.%20This%20is%20top-tier%20cancellation%20that%20stacks%20up%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20pairs%20available%2C%20seeming%20to%20suck%20the%20air%20out%20of%20the%20world%20and%20plant%20you%20in%20an%20isolation%20chamber%20of%20solace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%20feature%20indoors%20with%20studio%20speakers%20playing%20sound%20effects%20as%20well%20as%20outdoors%20on%20hikes%20and%20dog%20walks%2C%20where%20it%20was%20most%20impressive.%20Tapping%20the%20button%20can%20almost%20extinguish%20the%20world%2C%20from%20city%20din%20to%20chirping%20birds.%20Even%20traffic-laden%20streets%20glide%20into%20a%20soft%20whisper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20head-to-head%20tests%2C%20only%20Bose's%20mighty%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20outpowered%20them%2C%20reducing%20sounds%20like%20keystrokes%20and%20drone%20effects%20to%20an%20even%20lower%20murmur.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20Ace's%20ability%20to%20offer%20such%20stark%20silence%20without%20a%20modicum%20of%20added%20white%20noise%20makes%20them%20a%20contender%20for%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-noise-cancelling-headphones%5C%22%3Ebest%20noise-canceling%20headphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20can%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace%20also%20have%20an%20excellent%20transparency%20mode%20that's%20designed%20to%20let%20in%20environmental%20sounds%20to%20keep%20you%20aware.%20This%20mode%20is%20vividly%20clear%20and%20natural.%20It's%20so%20good%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20wear%20them%20virtually%20all%20day%20without%20skipping%20a%20beat%2C%20similar%20to%20Apple's%20latest%20AirPods.%20Though%20we%20weren't%20able%20to%20test%20the%20Ace%20directly%20against%20the%20AirPods%20Max%2C%20based%20on%20previous%20listening%2C%20we're%20confident%20you%20won't%20find%20a%20more%20natural-sounding%20transparency%20mode%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20one%20notable%20caveat%20to%20our%20praise.%20With%20this%20mode%20engaged%2C%20we%20occasionally%20heard%20mild%20connection%20noise%20in%20the%20right%20earcup.%20Sonos%20sent%20us%20two%20models%20to%20test%20and%20this%20issue%20was%20present%20on%20both.%20It's%20not%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20nuisance%20in%20most%20scenarios%20(it's%20audible%20only%20when%20connecting%20for%20a%20call%20or%20between%20songs%20in%20a%20quiet%20room)%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20disappointing%20from%20headphones%20this%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20debut%20products%20to%20arrive%20with%20a%20few%20bugs%2C%20so%20this%20could%20be%20ironed%20out%20with%20firmware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Additional%20features%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ace's%20lack%20of%20WiFi%20streaming%20is%20disappointing%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20get%20TV%20Swap%20to%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221615%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sonos%20Ace%20headphones%20are%20shown%20on%20an%20Arc%20soundbar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6663820ded9a404d829be4e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221211%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ace's%20TV%20Swap%20feature%20is%20supposed%20to%20let%20you%20send%20audio%20from%20an%20Arc%20soundbar%20to%20the%20headphones.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ace%20have%20many%20top%20features%20you'd%20expect%20from%20flagship%20noise-canceling%20headphones%2C%20like%20multi-point%20pairing%2C%20sensors%20to%20pause%20audio%20when%20you%20take%20them%20off%2C%20and%20various%20other%20settings%20from%20within%20the%20Sonos%20app.%20Their%20battery%20life%20of%20up%20to%2030%20hours%20per%20charge%20is%20highly%20competitive%2C%20and%20we%20could%20use%20them%20all%20day%20for%20multiple%20days%20without%20the%20need%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Ace's%20inability%20to%20group%20with%20other%20Sonos%20speakers%20to%20stream%20music%20and%20other%20audio%20sources%20over%20WiFi%20is%20something%20of%20a%20letdown%2C%20even%20if%20it%20would%20have%20been%20unique%20among%20their%20peers.%20It's%20not%20particularly%20surprising%20at%20this%20price%20%E2%80%94%20we%20would%20have%20expected%20another%20%24100%20or%20so%20added%20in%20to%20get%20seamless%20support%20for%20both%20WiFi%20and%20Bluetooth%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20does%20put%20the%20Ace%20in%20a%20somewhat%20siloed%20position%20within%20the%20Sonos%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consolation%20prize%20for%20the%20Sonos%20faithful%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20wirelessly%20switch%20audio%20between%20the%20Ace%20headphones%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-arc-soundbar-review%5C%22%3ESonos%20Arc%20soundbar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(and%20eventually%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2d5cb8c49f38df4b3ef60ee73be9de5b460eaeaf0d0b70a731ae234f3f349dc8%26postID%3D6663095ee01a10ede1c25f21%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Beam-Gen-2-Black%252Fdp%252FB09GPYL7BJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dee86734b931b53715ef3c3a98df90eeb810b8f2796e11042a05accb9c239ccc8%26postID%3D6663095ee01a10ede1c25f21%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Essential-Soundbar-Music-Video%252Fdp%252FB0B2KQFTG9%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERay%3C%2Fa%3E).%20This%20is%20handled%20via%20a%20TV%20Swap%20button%20in%20the%20Sonos%20app%2C%20currently%20for%20iOS%20users%20only.%20This%20means%20you%20can%20hear%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20privately%20through%20the%20headphones%20without%20disturbing%20others.%20And%20this%20mode%20supports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%3EDolby%20Atmos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20you%20can%20get%20a%20surround%20sound%20effect%20through%20the%20headphones.%20But%20even%20with%20an%20iPhone%20and%20a%20new%20Sonos%20Arc%20soundbar%20on%20hand%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20times%20we%20tried%2C%20we%20couldn't%20get%20either%20pair%20of%20Ace%20headphones%20Sonos%20sent%20us%20to%20sync%20with%20the%20Arc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESonos'%20support%20team%20told%20us%20%26quot%3BYou've%20encountered%20a%20rare%20bug%20that%20our%20team%20is%20aware%20of%20and%20working%20to%20address%20in%20a%20future%20release.%26quot%3B%20The%20headphones%20use%20a%205GHz%20connection%20for%20this%20feature%20(despite%20their%20lack%20of%20full%20WiFi%20support)%2C%20so%20it's%20possible%20our%20network%20played%20a%20part.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20could%20easily%20group%20the%20Arc%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4eb9b15317e19f102f40628b58b2940d9a200f36e514e4476d1adc1bd90e1542%26postID%3D6663095ee01a10ede1c25f21%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Era-100-Wireless-Speaker%252Fdp%252FB0BW34LCB8%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Era%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D84a14f8805f39e185301ebcdd805b8500e7fa13faf71b6229a9c74dcf9393be4%26postID%3D6663095ee01a10ede1c25f21%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsonos-ace-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSonos-Era-300-Wireless-Speaker%252Fdp%252FB0BW2LV57K%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEra%20300%3C%2Fa%3E%20speaker%20for%20multi-room%20playback%20made%20the%20issue%20all%20the%20more%20curious%20(and%20frustrating).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20expect%20a%20firmware%20update%20to%20address%20this%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20Sonos%2C%20after%20all%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we'll%20update%20this%20review%20with%20any%20changes%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20them%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Sonos%20Ace%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sonos%20Ace%20h