f%20about%2080%20people%20outside%20the%20venue%20who%20had%20also%20just%20realized%20they%20weren't%20getting%20to%20see%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-mom-seeing-taylor-swift-in-europe-with-kids-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehottest%20concerts%20of%20the%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa576b2d-2830-47fe-a6fb-189e5412a5f6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20group%20of%20disappointed%20fans%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20night%20around%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chappelle%20Roan%20in%20concert%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666093d0cc442a2f676e2d3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20see%20Chapelle%20Roan%20live%2C%20but%20we%20made%20the%20most%20of%20our%20night.%20%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Hill%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20venue%2C%20our%20group%20of%20upset%20people%20with%20worthless%20tickets%20decided%20to%20find%20something%20else%20to%20do%20together.%20After%20all%2C%20we'd%20gotten%20dressed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20we%20were%20in%20a%20caravan%20of%20around%2030%20mermaids%20making%20our%20way%20to%20the%20nearest%20bar.%20Someone%20got%20the%20bartender%20to%20play%20Chappell%20Roan's%20discography%20and%20ordered%20us%20all%20a%20round%20of%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20ensued%20was%20a%20night%20of%20singing%20and%20dancing%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40chappellroan%2Fvideo%2F7364553193529052462%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bfavorite%20artist's%20favorite%20artist%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20cursing%20third-party%20ticket%20vendors%2C%20and%20making%20new%20friends.%20As%20others%20learned%20their%20tickets%20were%20useless%20that%20night%2C%20they%20found%20out%20about%20our%20impromptu%20party%20and%20joined%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20this%20experience%2C%20I%20would've%20probably%20had%20a%20miserable%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220730bef5-2ed0-4919-a9e6-d72a26f9803f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20got%20my%20money%20back%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20disappointed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20thinks%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-buying-fake-item-amazon-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20enough%20not%20to%20get%20duped%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20they%20are%20%E2%80%94%20including%20me.%20I%20was%20mortified%2C%20but%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20people%20I%20met%20who%20had%20also%20bought%20tickets%20that%20wouldn't%20work%20helped%20me%20realize%20there%20wasn't%20much%20we%20could've%20done%20to%20avoid%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20tickets%20from%20what%20I%20consider%20to%20be%20a%20more%20reputable%20resale%20platform%2C%20not%20some%20random%20person%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20or%20Craigslist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20case%2C%20SeatGeek%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.seatgeek.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360007200174-Can-I-trust-the-tickets-sold-on-SeatGeek%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuyer%20Guarantee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20was%20quickly%20issued%20a%20full%20refund.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20missed%20out%20on%20something%20that%20I%20paid%20to%20travel%20over%201%2C000%20miles%20to%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20another%20part%20of%20the%20conversation%20about%20how%20flawed%20ticketing%20for%20live%20events%20has%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Taylor%20Swift%20fans%20who%20got%20nonexistent%20tickets%20to%20The%20Eras%20Tour%20faced%20issues%20similar%20to%20mine%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstubhub-ticket-fraud-eras-tour-taylor-swift-tickets-didnt-exist-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%20to%20get%20refunds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20filed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-ticketmaster-fiasco-doj-lawsuit-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantitrust%20lawsuit%20against%20Live%20Nation%20Entertainment%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20parent%20company%20of%20Ticketmaster)%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20unlawfully%20dominating%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeatGeek%20has%20not%20explained%20to%20me%20what%20went%20wrong%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20I'll%20ever%20know%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20odd%20that%20someone%20could%20just%20send%20me%20a%20link%2C%20and%20I'd%20get%20their%20tickets.%20Maybe%20the%20original%20tickets%20were%20real%20but%20the%20seller%20never%20fully%20transferred%20them%20to%20me%20at%20all.%20Or%20maybe%20they%20were%20really%20good%20fakes%20all%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20I've%20taken%20away%20from%20this%20experience%20is%20that%20it's%20easy%20to%20get%20unscannable%20tickets%20that%20look%20legitimate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20crucial%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20obtain%20possession%20of%20the%20original%20event%20tickets%20if%20they%20were%20initially%20sold%20through%20Ticketmaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20though%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20buying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-leaving-us-first-time-for-taylor-swift-eras-tour-uk-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etickets%20for%20a%20concert%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20unless%20I%20can%20absolutely%20guarantee%20I%20will%20get%20in%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20SeatGeek%20issued%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20sorry%20that%20this%20fan%20wasn't%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20show%20and%20understand%20the%20disappointment%20and%20frustration%20this%20whole%20experience%20must%20have%20caused.%20Up