o%20make%20sure%20there%20were%20no%20glaring%20red%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20without%20being%20able%20to%20see%20the%20house%20in%20person%2C%20any%20cosmetic%20issues%20we%20couldn't%20see%20on%20the%20video%20call%20would%20be%20worth%20it%20to%20have%20the%20features%20of%20this%20house%20while%20staying%20within%20our%20budget.%20And%20I%20felt%20secure%20that%20major%20issues%20would%20be%20caught%20by%20an%20inspector%20before%20closing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20made%20an%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20got%20caught%20in%20a%20bidding%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20a%20risky%20and%20somewhat%20unconventional%20decision%20to%20put%20an%20offer%20on%20the%20house%20almost%20sight%20unseen.%20The%20longer%20the%20day%20stretched%20waiting%20to%20hear%20if%20it%20was%20accepted%2C%20the%20more%20attached%20I%20became%20to%20the%20house%20we'd%20only%20seen%20virtually%20and%20in%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20another%20family%20had%20also%20put%20an%20offer%20on%20the%20house%20and%20it%20was%20very%20close%20to%20ours.%20My%20heart%20sank%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20have%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbidding-war%5C%22%3Ebidding%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20we%20wanted%20our%20house.%20Our%20competition%20responded%20first.%20They%20wanted%20to%20keep%20their%20offer%20as%20it%20was%20but%20waived%20their%20right%20to%20have%20the%20house%20inspected%20before%20closing.%20They%20decided%20to%20gamble%20on%20the%20home%20having%20no%20structural%2C%20plumbing%2C%20or%20otherwise%20unseen%20problems%20that%20the%20seller%20might%20be%20liable%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20discussed%20whether%20this%20was%20a%20risk%20we%20were%20also%20willing%20to%20take%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20we%20could%20not%20take%20the%20chance%20that%20a%20home%20we'd%20never%20even%20seen%20before%20would%20also%20not%20have%20any%20big%20problems.%20Instead%20of%20waiving%20an%20inspection%2C%20we%20offered%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20the%20appraisal%20price%20%E2%80%94%20%248%2C000%20more.%20As%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%20lender%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20only%20loan%20us%20the%20money%20for%20the%20home's%20appraised%20value%2C%20that%20money%20would%20come%20directly%20from%20our%20pockets%20with%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20home%20inspector%20missed%20a%20crack%20in%20our%20foundation%2C%20but%20he%20was%20financially%20responsible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sellers%20accepted%20our%20offer%2C%20and%20we%20were%20on%20our%20way%20to%20owning%20a%20home%20with%20virtually%20everything%20we%20wanted.%20Once%20we%20were%20in%20Kansas%2C%20my%20husband%20accompanied%20a%20professional%20inspector%20into%20our%20home-to-be.%20On%20the%20surface%2C%20it%20was%20exactly%20as%20we%20expected.%20Even%20better%2C%20the%20inspector%20didn't%20find%20any%20underlying%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20we%20wondered%20if%20we%20should%20have%20also%20waived%20our%20inspection%20and%20saved%20that%20money.%20But%20we%20reassured%20each%20other%20that%20we%20had%20done%20the%20responsible%20thing%20by%20deciding%20to%20pay%20more%20money%20instead.%20And%20we%20were%20absolutely%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20one%20week%20of%20moving%20in%2C%20Ian%20was%20in%20our%20basement%20laundry%20room%2C%20the%20only%20unfinished%20part%20of%20the%20basement.%20He%20noticed%20light%20coming%20through%20a%20crack%20in%20the%20concrete%20wall%20and%20a%20gap%20near%20the%20basement%20window%20that%20indicated%20the%20surrounding%20earth%20had%20pushed%20the%20foundation%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Ian%20is%20not%20at%20all%20trained%20in%20construction%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhome-inspection%5C%22%3Ehome%20inspection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20knew%20this%20was%20a%20problem.%20In%20fact%2C%20while%20we%20were%20buying%20our%20house%2C%20a%20relative%20was%20having%20a%20similar%20foundation%20problem%20repaired%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%2415%2C000.%20Ian%20called%20the%20inspector%20we%20had%20hired%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20come%20back%20to%20take%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20his%20credit%2C%20when%20the%20inspector%20arrived%20and%20saw%20the%20gap%2C%20he%20immediately%20owned%20up%20to%20his%20mistake%20in%20missing%20this%20issue.%20He%20failed%20to%20check%20the%20outer%20perimeter%20of%20the%20foundation%20where%20he%20would%20have%20seen%20space%20between%20the%20foundation%20and%20the%20ground.%20This%20is%20a%20standard%20part%20of%20home%20inspection%2C%20and%20we're%20not%20sure%20why%20he%20skipped%20it.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20inspector%20said%20he%20would%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20fortifying%20the%20foundation%20and%20that%20if%20the%20damage%20was%20excessive%2C%20his%20insurance%20would%20buy%20the%20house%20from%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20today's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-mortgage-interest-rate%5C%22%3Eaverage%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20house%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20afford.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20relieved%20we%20decided%20not%20to%20waive%20our%20home%20inspection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20our%20inspector%20made%20a%20huge%20mistake%2C%20it%20is%20repairable%2C%20and%20I%20really%20can't%20say%20if%20knowing%20about%20it%20would%20have%20changed%20our%20decision%20to%20close%20on%20the%20house.%20And%20even%20though%20my%20husband%20saw%20the%20foundation%20problem%20and%20not%20the%20inspector%2C%20by%20having%20a%20third%20party%20contractually%20responsible%20for%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20house%2C%20we%20were%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20repair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20tough%20housing%20market%2C%20doing%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20be%20a%20competitive%20buyer%20can%20be%20tempting.%20Waiving%20an%20inspection%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20viable%20way%20to%20outbid%20other%20potential%20buyers%20without%20increasing%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20spend%20at%20closing.%20I'm%20sure%20people%20take%20this%20risk%20and%20get%20lucky.%20But%20unless%20you%20have%20the%20money%20to%20address%20any%20potential%20problems%20you%20discover%20after%20closing%2C%20waiving%20an%20inspection%20should%20be%20where%20you%20draw%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20new%20home%20buyers%20is%20to%20save%20a%20little%20more%20than%20you%20expect%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20down%20payment%20so%20you%20can%20make%20a%20more%20competitive%20monetary%20bid%20without%20compromising%20safety%20and%20security%20in%20your%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-more-than-home-appraised-value-guarantee-inspection-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717796941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F625471993df5750019f73199%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-more-than-home-appraised-value-guarantee-inspection-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Instead%20of%20waiving%20her%20right%20to%20a%20home%20inspection%2C%20writer%20Sarah%20Martinez%20Shaw%20offered%20more%20than%20her%20home's%20appraised%20value%20to%20win%20a%20bidding%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Martinez%20Shaw)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-more-than-home-app