3Cli%3EDunkin's%20doughnut%20was%20dense%20and%20cake-like%2C%20while%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20was%20lighter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKrispy%20Kreme%20and%20Dunkin'%20are%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20doughnut%20chains%2C%20but%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20out%20which%20one%20had%20the%20best%20glazed%20doughnut.%20So%20I%20set%20out%20to%20do%20my%20own%20taste%20test%20to%20see%20which%20one%20was%20the%20victor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20pure%20number%20perspective%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20doughnuts%20reign%20supreme.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dunkindonuts.com%2Fen%2Fabout%2Fabout-us%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFranchising%2520Company%2520Snapshot-%2CCOMPANY%2520SNAPSHOT%2CInspire%2520Brands%2520family%2520of%2520restaurants.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13%2C000%20Dunkin'%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20world%20while%20Krispy%20Kreme%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.krispykreme.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-details%2F2024%2FKrispy-Kreme-Reports-First-Quarter-2024-Financial-Results-and-Reaffirms-Full-Year-2024-Guidance%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C400%20retailers%20worldwide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20doughnut%20shops%20and%20partnerships%20with%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dunkin's%20profits%20aren't%20public%2C%20Krispy%20Kreme%2C%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.krispykreme.com%2Ffinancials%2Fquarterly-results%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20its%20net%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%205.7%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20year%20to%20%24442.7%20million%2C%20according%20to%20their%20quarterly%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20pure%20stats%20wouldn't%20help%20me%2C%20I%20visited%20both%20chains%20and%20now%20I%20can%20see%20why%20the%20latter%20is%20h