rs%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Midea%20U%20has%20a%20remote%20control%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20Midea%20Air%20app%20was%20more%20user-friendly%20and%20connected%20seamlessly%20to%20my%20Android%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20Use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Midea%20U%20has%20an%20inverter%20compressor%20with%20a%20variable-speed%20motor%20that%20makes%20slight%20adjustments%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20target%20temperature.%20Most%20ACs%20just%20cycle%20on%20and%20off.%20The%20constant%20low-level%20operation%20of%20the%20inverter%20compressor%20is%20much%20more%20efficient.%20That's%20why%20it%20earned%20Energy%20Star's%20%26quot%3BMost%20Efficient%26quot%3B%20certification%3B%20one%20of%20the%20first%20ACs%20to%20earn%20this%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20a%20smart%20plug%20to%20measure%20how%20much%20energy%20it%20consumed%20over%2024%20hours.%20Running%20on%20high%2C%20it%20consumed%209.6%20kWh%2C%20which%20works%20out%20to%200.4%20kWh%20per%20hour.%20This%20was%20better%20than%20most%20of%20the%20ACs%20I've%20tested.%20If%20you%20run%20the%20Midea%20on%20high%20for%20eight%20hours%20daily%20all%20summer%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20pay%20about%20%2449%20for%20electricity%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fregions%2Fmidwest%2Fdata%2Faverageenergyprices_selectedareas_table.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20US%20average%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20pretty%20reasonable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECooling%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20cooling%20performance%2C%20I%20run%20an%20air%20conditioner%20on%20high%20for%20an%20hour%20in%20a%20650-square-foot%20room.%20Then%2C%20I%20compare%20the%20before%20and%20after%20readings%20of%20a%20digital%20thermometer%20positioned%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Midea%20U%20Inverter%20AC%20lowered%20the%20room's%20temperature%20by%201.7%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20which%20is%20impressive%20considering%20its%20minimal%20energy%20use%2C%20but%20only%20average%20among%20the%20units%20I've%20tested.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20in%20cooling%20mode%2C%20the%20Midea%20U%20also%20removes%20moisture%20and%20circulates%20the%20air%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20room%20feel%20even%20cooler.%20As%20you%20run%20it%20longer%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20room's%20temperature%20will%20continue%20to%20decrease%2C%20though%20at%20a%20slower%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20sits%20on%20a%20couch%20reading%20a%20magazine%20with%20the%20Midea%20U-Shaped%20AC%20displayed%20in%20a%20window%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dd13dfbd8c0900184e5de2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20quiet%20operation%20of%20the%20Midea%20U%20makes%20it%20great%20for%20bedrooms%20and%20other%20areas%20where%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20noise%20at%20a%20minimum.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Midea%20U%20is%20the%20air%20conditioner%20to%20buy%20if%20you%20want%20silence%20while%20sleeping.%20A%20sound%20meter%20positioned%206%20feet%20from%20the%20unit%20registered%2048%20decibels%20while%20it%20ran%20on%20high%2C%20a%20little%20lower%20than%20a%20refrigerator%20running%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20best%20I've%20tested.%C2%A0%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20most%20compressors%20shift%20between%20off%20and%20on%2C%20they%20will%20make%20a%20startling%20sound.%20The%20Midea%20U%20didn't%20have%20this%20issue.%20The%20inverter%20compressor%20shifted%20seamlessly%20between%20speeds.%20It%20wasn't%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmart%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Midea%20U's%20control%20panel