%2C%20the%20Arena%20Group%20lost%20the%20rights%20to%20publish%20SI%2C%20its%20best-known%20brand%2C%20after%20the%205-Hour%20Energy%20creator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanaj-bhargava-arena-group-sports-illustrated-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManoj%20Bhargava%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20over%20Arena%20and%20missed%20a%20licensing%20payment%20to%20Authentic%20Brands%20Group.%20ABG%20awarded%20the%20publishing%20license%20to%20Minute%20Media%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanoj-bhargava-sued-by-sports-illustrated-owners-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20Bhargava%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2449%20million%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20acting%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bgangster%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Bhargava%20and%20his%20company%20hit%20back%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20seeking%20%24200%20million%20for%20what%20they%20claim%20was%20a%20plot%20by%20ABG%20and%20Minute%20Media%20to%20string%20the%20Arena%20Group%20along%20while%20making%20copies%20of%20its%20websites%20and%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20to%20poach%20its%20employees%20and%20biggest%20spenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BABG%20deceived%20Arena%20by%20promising%20to%20work%20with%20Arena%20in%20good%20faith%20to%20renegotiate%20Arena's%20license%20so%20as%20to%20allow%20Arena%20to%20continue%20to%20operate%20Sports%20Illustrated%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24738015-bhargava-and-arena-group-counterclaim%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20complaint%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BPrivately%2C%20ABG%20and%20Minute%20had%20been%20partnered%20for%20weeks%2C%20conspiring%20to%20steal%20Arena's%20code%20and%20publisher%20relationships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20countersuit%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20CVC%20Capital%20Partners%20and%20BlackRock%2C%20investors%20in%20ABG%2C%20though%20they%20weren't%20named%20as%20parties%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20In%20the%20complaint%20and%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20Steve%20Janisse%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20Arena%20and%20Bhargava%2C%20said%20it%20was%20unethical%20for%20them%20to%20have%20assisted%20in%20what%20Arena%20and%20Bhargava%20characterized%20as%20ABG's%20sham%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing%20that%20CVC%20Capital%20and%20BlackRock%20would%20condone%20this%20type%20of%20corporate%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20Janisse%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20we're%20surprised%20they%20aren't%20calling%20for%20a%20change%20of%20leadership%20at%20ABG.%26quot%3B%20An%20executive%20at%20CVC%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20emails%2C%20and%20a%20representative%20for%20BlackRock%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhargava%20has%20a%20history%20of%20aggressive%20legal%20action.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fclareoconnor%2F2012%2F02%2F08%2Fmanoj-bhargava-the-mystery-monk-making-billions-with-5-hour-energy%2F%3Fsh%3D1632f03f27ae%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2012%20Forbes%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20he%20had%20already%20filed%20more%20than%2090%20lawsuits.%20Bhargava%2C%20who%20made%20his%20billions%20selling%205-Hour%20Energy%20drinks%2C%20showed%20the%20Forbes%20reporter%20a%20%26quot%3Bcemetery%26quot%3B%20bookcase%20in%20his%20office%2C%20lined%20with%20energy-shot%20bottles%20from%20competitors%20his%20company%20had%20sued%20or%20legally%20bullied%20out%20of%20the%20market%2C%20calling%20them%20the%20gravestones%20of%20his%20vanquished%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhargava's%20lawsuit%20adds%20to%20the%20morass%20of%20legal%20actions%20that%20have%20formed%20around%20the%20Arena%20Group.%20In%20early%20April%2C%20ABG%20sued%20Arena%20and%20Bhargava%20over%20the%20missed%20licensing%20payment%20and%20a%20%2445%20million%20termination%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArena%2C%20whose%20stock%20trades%20for%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20it%20did%20at%20th