%20are%20his%20best%20tips%20for%20selecting%20more%20%26quot%3Bpotentially%20healthy%20ultra-processed%20foods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c05afe3c-c473-470c-b13f-1c965975328c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20assume%20all%20ultra-processed%20foods%20are%20created%20equal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22processed%20food%20cheese%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cdef60a021b4c196824f622%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221225%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECategorizing%20a%20food%20as%20%26quot%3Bultra-processed%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20tell%20you%20which%20nutrients%20are%20in%20it.%20%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMorry%20Gash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECategorizing%20a%20food%20as%20an%20ultra-processed%20food%20doesn't%20technically%20tell%20you%20anything%20about%20the%20nutrients%20in%20that%20particular%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20use%20a%20system%20for%20classifying%20UPFs%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-a-completely-unprocessed-food-diet-benefits-drawbacks-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENOVA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20in%202009.%20The%20NOVA%20system%20divides%20foods%20we%20eat%20into%20four%20basic%20categories%2C%20based%20on%20their%20level%20of%20processing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENOVA%201%3A%20completely%20unprocessed%20items%20like%20plants%20and%20animal%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20minimally%20processed%20items%20that%20have%20not%20been%20preserved%20or%20seasoned%20in%20any%20way%2C%20like%20a%20fresh-pressed%20juice%2C%20dried%20herb%2C%20or%20unsweetened%20yogurt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENOVA%202%3A%20called%20%26quot%3Bculinary%20ingredients%2C%26quot%3B%20these%20are%20natural%20items%20that%20have%20been%20crushed%20or%20processed%20for%20seasoning%20food%2C%20like%20oils%2C%20syrups%2C%20honey%2C%20butter%20or%20lard%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20corn%20starch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENOVA%203%3A%20any%20food%20that%20is%20combined%2C%20cooked%2C%20altered%2C%20preserved%2C%20pickled%20or%20seasoned%20in%20any%20way.%20This%20could%20be%20anything%20from%20a%20fresh%20homemade%20bread%2C%20to%20canned%20beans%2C%20salted%20nuts%2C%20cheese%2C%20or%20pickles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENOVA%204%3A%20ultra-processed%20foods%20and%20ready-to-eat%20items%20that%20can%20only%20be%20made%20in%20a%20factory.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20NOVA%20is%20all%20about%20how%20the%20food%20is%20made.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20give%20any%20consideration%20to%20the%20composition%20of%20fat%2C%20sugar%2C%20protein%2C%20carbohydrates%2C%20calories%2C%20vitamins%2C%20and%20fiber%20in%20a%20given%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22671%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22muffin%20eating%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6663375ed0b8e1c832cd251f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYIUCHEUNG%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20worries%20that%20if%20we%20all%20become%20hyper-focused%20on%20categorizing%20foods%20into%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunhealthy%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20their%20NOVA%20number%2C%20we're%20missing%20a%20larger%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20you%20can%20make%20rich%20and%20irresistible%20ice%20cream%20at%20home%2C%20or%20have%20an%20ultra-processed%20vegetable%20stir%20fry%20that%20comes%20in%20a%20plastic%20bag%20but%20has%20way%20more%20fiber%20and%20vitamins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20those%20NOVA%204%20products%20are%20high%20in%20all%20the%20good%20things%20and%20low%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20bad%20things%20that%20we%20traditionally%20think%20of%20in%20terms%20of%20nutrition%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20argue%20that%20that%20%3Cem%3Eprobably%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20being%20a%20healthy%20ultra-processed%20food.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20a%20ready-to-heat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.truefood.tech%2Fproduct%2Ftg_52099477%3Fstore%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrozen%20dinner%20in%20a%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20includes%20spinach%2C%20red%20bell%20peppers%2C%20garbanzo%20beans%20and%20quinoa%20%E2%80%94%20while%20it%20is%20definitely%20an%20ultra-processed%20food%20that's%20been%20manufactured%20with%20stabilizers%20like%20xanthan%20gum%20in%20it%20%E2%80%94%20still%20likely%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20nutrition%20packed%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20basically%20doing%20is%20we're%20using%20everything%20else%20that%20we've%20learned%20in%20nutrition%20science%20and%20applying%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F385%2Fbmj-2023-078476%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20seems%20to%20support%20this%20eating%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20it%20suggested%20that%20ultra-processed%20meats%2C%20sugary%20beverages%20like%20soda%2C%20and%20sweets%20(desserts%2C%20sugary%20cereals)%20may%20be%20more%20dangerous%20than%20other%20ultra-processed%20options%2C%20and%20they're%20linked%20to%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20early%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af6d1869-e799-40c4-a126-69bc8438bf69%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20things%20to%20look%20for%20in%20ultra-processed%20foods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bowl%20of%20oatmeal%20with%20pumpkin%2C%20pumpkin%20seeds%2C%20and%20cinnamon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e4d004ca513d8242dcc3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhole-grain%20oats%2C%20seeds%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20veggies%20are%20great%20options.%20%3Cp%3EVeselovaElena%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20Hall%20says%2C%20pick%20ultra-processed%20foods%20with%20lots%20of%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhole%20grains%20(could%20be%20quinoa%2C%20oats%2C%20or%20brown%20rice)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENon-starchy%20vegetables%20(like%20broccoli%2C%20spinach%2C%20or%20green%20beans)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELegumes%20(including%20beans%2C%20lentils%2C%20and%20peanuts)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20avoid%20foods%20that%20are%20high%20in%20saturated%20fat%2C%20added%20sugar%2C%20and%20sodium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalt%20can%20be%20especially%20hard%20to%20avoid.%20It's%20a%20handy%20preservative%20and%20flavor-amplifier%20abundant%20in%20many%20UPFs.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20still%20a%20little%20too%20high%20in%20sodium%2C%20but%20you%20can%20try%20to%20choose%20better%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229118b8b4-12f0-4437-8e8d-de588bc24a20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20it%20your%20mission%20to%20increase%20your%20vegetable%20intake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221471%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vegetables%20in%20stir%20fry%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666337f7cc442a2f676f30bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22981%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bowl%20of%20packaged%20oatmeal%20for%20breakfast%20or%20a%20high-protein%20bean%20and%20cheese%20burrito%20from%20the%20freezer%20aisle%20for%20dinner%20won't%20be%20the%20end%20of%20your%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20there%20is%20a%20whole-food%20option%2C%20go%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20see%20it%20as%20a%20treat%2C%20a%20burst%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-longevity-supplements-vs-exercise-and-diet-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutrients%20to%20fuel%20your%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20is%20currently%20studying%20the%20health%20benefits%20of%20adding%20a%20side%20salad%20or%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-tips-man-lost-40-pounds-10-inches-walking-nutrients-order-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-starchy%20veggies%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20processed%20meal.%20He%20has%20a%20hunch%20that%20it%20may%20help%20to%20blunt%20some%20of%20the%20harms%20of%20ultra-processed%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he's%20also%20a%20busy%2C%20working%20parent%20and%20he%20%E2%80%94%20like%20so%20many%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20is%20just%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20best%20he%20can%20with%20the%20money%2C%20time%2C%20and%20knowledge%20he%20has%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20it%20be%20better%20if%20you%20had%20made%20the%20homemade%20version%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20wonders.%20%26quot%3BMaybe.%20It's%20possible%20that%20there's%20some%20weird%20additive%20or%20something%2C%20an%20ingredient%20in%20that%20food%20that%20is%20not%20good%20for%20you.%20We%20don't%20have%20the%20science%20on%20that%20yet%2C%20but%20applying%20what%20we%20do%20know%2C%20I%20think%20you%20can%20still%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-to-cut-down-on-upfs-3-questions-to-ask-yourself-dietitian-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducated%20choices%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-ultra-processed-foods-may-be-healthier-than-homemade-scientist-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717784893000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66633a38d0b8e1c832cd291c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-ultra-processed-foods-may-be-healthier-than-homemade-scientist-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ultra-processed%20foods%20vary%20widely%20in%20their%20nutrition.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20store-bought%20stir%20fry%20may%20be%20better%20for%20you%20than%20homemade%20ice%20cream.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrue