se%20the%20cabling%20cost%20as%20the%20whole%20system%20would%20be%20drawn%20to%20your%20house%20including%20the%20net%20metre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20viable%20proposition%20for%20apartment%20owners%20and%20tenants%20with%20rental%20agreements%20for%2010%20or%2015%20years.%20Tenants%20cannot%20remove%20the%20setup%20to%20take%20it%20somewhere%20else%20because%20it%20will%20again%20involve%20paperwork%20and%20installation%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2212%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20assume%20the%20monthly%20power%20expenses%20to%20be%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20installation%20and%20inverter%20(with%20a%2010-year%20warranty)%20to%20be%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20So%2C%20for%20a%2015-year%20contract%2C%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20will%20be%20generated%20only%20after%20five%20years%20and%20residents%20can%20avail%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20free%20electricity%20provided%20the%20inverter%20lasts%20for%20say%2013%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20landlord%20will%20incur%20the%20capital%20cost%20for%20the%20new%20inverter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Using%20balconies%20could%20not%20be%20very%20feasible%20if%20the%20energy%20generation%20will%20be%20small-scale%20compared%20to%20the%20requirement.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20safety%20risks%20from%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20lightning%20strikes%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20cyclones%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKiran%20points%20out%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20involved%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20boards.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20contract%20term%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20provider%20and%20the%20subsidy.%20The%20service%20provider%20and%20the%20solar%20installation%20companies%20will%20help%20do%20the%20paperwork%20but%20ensure%20that%20you%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2215%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20further%20asks%20residents%20to%20consider%20the%20maths%20on%20subsequent%20savings.%20If%20your%20monthly%20power%20bill%20is%20Rs%202%2C500%20in%20a%202BHK%2C%20then%20you%20will%20recover%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20installation%20in%2010%20years%20(assuming%20rooftop%20cable%20wiring%20expenses%20in%20addition%20to%20inverter%20and%20installation%20costs%20totaling%20Rs%203%20lakh).%20It%20does%20not%20make%20sense%20if%20the%20monthly%20bill%20is%20Rs%201%2C000-1%2C200%20and%20tenants%20move%20out%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Photo%20credit%3A%20Adobe%20stock%20images%2C%20Bhoomi%20Arkade%2C%20and%20Palash%20Co-Operative%20Housing%20Society)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717591462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1717589888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352016%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Want%20to%20harness%20solar%20energy%20in%20your%20apartment%20and%20save%20on%20monthly%20electricity%20bills%3F%20Experts%20share%2015%20factors%20to%20consider%20for%20solar%20panel%20installation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Bottles%20Decompose%20in%20180%20Days%20%26amp%3B%20Look%20Like%20They%E2%80%99re%20Made%20of%20Plastic!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20storing%20water%20to%20juices%20and%20various%20other%20daily%20essentials%2C%20plastic%20containers%20have%20become%20ubiquitous%20in%20our%20surroundings.%20Despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F202988%2Fchildrens-day-kids-fighting-climate-change-plastic-air-pollution-delhi-ncr-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewe%20see%20little%20change%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20in%20landfills.%20While%20many%20states%20have%20enforced%20bans%20on%20single-use%20plastic%2C%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20remain%20a%20common%20source%20of%20plastic%20waste%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EMoneycontrol%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CApproximately%202.8%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20bottle%20waste%20goes%20uncollected%20annually.%20The%20environmental%20impact%20is%20significant.%20Macroplastics%2C%20including%20PET%2C%20often%20clog%20sewage%20systems%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%2C%20pollute%20rivers%2C%20lakes%2C%20and%20beaches%2C%20and%20degrade%20the%20aesthetic%20and%20ecological%20value%20of%20tourist%20destinations%20and%20landscapes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20combat%20the%20escalating%20issue%20of%20plastic%20waste%2C%20many%20individuals%20and%20changemakers%20have%20devised%20various%20solutions.%20Among%20these%20innovators%20is%20Nikhil%20Kumar%20of%20Greenevon%20Bio%20Bottles%2C%20who%20has%20pioneered%20a%20bottle%20made%20from%20sugarcane!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bottle%20is%20100%25%20biodegradable%20and%20100%25%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331134%2Fgujarat-sustainable-startup-reroute-makes-ecofriendly-shoes-from-sugarcane-plastic-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20made%20using%20sugarcane%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20bottles%20are%20environment%20friendly%20and%20only%20take%20180%20days%20to%20degrade%20when%20exposed%20to%20moisture%20and%20high%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nik