C3%A0-vis%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20sell%20them%20either%20stored%20in%20the%20open%20or%20tucked%20into%20ice%20bags.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20optics%20of%20flaunting%20a%20cooler%2C%20it%20is%20the%20purity%20and%20hygiene%20associated%20with%20a%20refrigerated%20cooler%20that%20influences%20consumer%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20retailers%20through%20the%20Superpower%20Retailer%20Program%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Prasad%2C%20a%20retailer%20on%20Park%20Street%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20says%20that%20introducing%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20has%20helped%20reshape%20his%20business%2C%20enabling%20him%20to%20stock%20up%20more%20products%2C%20all%20resulting%20in%20more%20sales.%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Pathak%20says%20beverage%20sales%20have%20soared%20since%20the%20installation%20of%20Coca-Cola%20India%20coolers%2C%20which%20keep%20the%20beverages%20refreshingly%20chilled%20and%20help%20attract%20more%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retail%20business%20owners%20with%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20in%20their%20kirana%20stores%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3