0charging%20mobile%20phones.%20This%20model%20was%20replicated%20across%20several%20countries%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibilities%20of%20digital%20technologies%20have%20now%20become%20further%20evident.%20With%20the%20remarkable%20advances%20in%20cooler%20technology%2C%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20stand%20out%20for%20their%20digital%20signage%20and%20enhanced%20design%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20an%20ongoing%20focus%20on%20replacing%20older%20ones%20with%20hydrofluorocarbon-free%20and%20more%20energy-efficient%20coolers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%20for%20Coca-Cola%2C%20in%202022%2C%2088%20percent%20of%20all%20new%20coolers%20placed%20were%20HFC-free.%20This%20is%20an%20increase%20from%2061%20percent%20of%20coolers%20placed%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20further%20builds%20on%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305877%2Fpernod-ricard-india-launches-one-for-our-planet-initiative-reduce-monocarton-packaging%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20society%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98Our%20Planet%20Matters%E2%80%99%20strategy.%20The%20bottom%20line%20of%20this%20is%20to%20bring%20transformational%20and%20radical%20change%20through%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20social%2C%20environmental%2C%20and%20economic%20stewardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20are%20being%20realised%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20the%20humble%20cooler%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20bringing%20more%20revenue%20to%20grassroots-level%20retailers%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20happiness%20quotient%20of%20customers%2C%20and%20enabling%20economies%20with%20a%20more%20vibrant%20retail%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717573465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%22%2C%22o